txt.en: 'Where is it that you come from?'
Register your heritage with the notary.
'Ah... a Stoor.\n\n'The Stoors were the last of the hobbit kindreds to come to the Shire, settling at last in the eastern marshlands of the Shire.'
Speak with Wistan Whitfoot, the hobbit notary
Wistan Whitfoot can be found in Michel Delving.
